==Continuity==
The [[2012]] reference book ''[[The Essential Reader's Companion]]'' dates the events of ''The Force Unleashed'' and [[Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II (novelization)|''The Force Unleashed II'']] to [[3 BBY/Legends|3 BBY]]&ndash;[[1 BBY/Legends|1 BBY]], placing them between the novels ''[[The Hutt Gambit]]'' ([[1997]]) and ''[[Lando Calrissian and the Mindharp of Sharu]]'' ([[1983]]).<ref name="ERC" />

